{"about_the_game":"<i>Malice &amp; Greed</i> is a roguelike turn-based RPG inspired by <i>Shin Megami Tensei &amp; Persona</i>, combined with elements of deckbuilders like <i>Slay the Spire</i>. Force <strong>every enemy &amp; boss </strong>to join your team, swapping allies in &amp; out during combat as you please!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566090/extras/AbductHeader.png?t=1710393505\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>After battle, the final defeated enemy <i><strong>joins you</strong></i>! Will you risk saving the strongest for last?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566090/extras/Abduct-April2022.gif?t=1710393505\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566090/extras/StealHeader.png?t=1710393505\" /><br></li><li><strong><i>Butcher</i></strong> enemies to steal their skills for yourself, and create the ultimate build!<br></li><li><strong><i>Fuse</i></strong> enemies together to customize them to your liking!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566090/extras/December-Butcher.gif?t=1710393505\" /><br><br></li><li>Mix &amp; match skills of <strong>4 Colors</strong> to explore new playstyles each run. You gain power each turn letting you use stronger skills as the fight goes on - but so does the enemy!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566090/extras/colorskills.png?t=1710393505\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566090/extras/TradeHeader.png?t=1710393505\" /><br></li><li>Sell unwanted allies to the <strong><i>Shady Smuggler</i></strong> to get powerful relics and upgrades!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_a